data.description: All Brick Home on 11 gorgeous acres in the coveted Homestead community just down the road from Cumberland Mtn. State Park with Swimming, Great Restaurant, Hiking, Canoeing, and of course  the Bear Trace Golf Course. 3BR brick home with wood floors, kitchen, dining area and living room. Access to the 11 acres also from Gentry Lane with many beautiful additional sites to build a new home or just enjoy all nature has to offer in your own Private woodlands. Buildings by shared driveway are included with property which include 1 car garage and partially finished apartment and wood working or hobby shop....All buildings to be emptied of stored items....
